    <body>
        <h1>Linking-You RDF Vocabulary</h1>

<p>Terms which link an organisation to common webpages, such as a contact page or "about" page.</p>      

<p>A few changes have been made to terms to make them useful outside academia. It is generally expected that the targets will be HTML documents, but in some cases it may be other formats, such as a PDF prospectus.</p>

<p>Namespace: <strong>http://purl.org/linkingyou/</strong></p>

<p>This vocublary is based on the 
<a href="http://lncn.eu/toolkit">Linking-You project</a> performed by those clever chaps at 
Lincoln University. This mapping <a href='http://linkingyou.blogs.lincoln.ac.uk/2012/11/20/linking-you-rdf-vocabulary/'>has been endorsed by the Lincoln team</a>. The RDF version of the linking-you toolkit was created by <a href="http://users.ecs.soton.ac.uk/cjg/">Christopher Gutteridge</a>.</p>

<p>View: <a href='http://openorg.ecs.soton.ac.uk/linkingyou/linkingyou.ttl'>Linking-You Vocabulary</a> (RDF Turtle).</p>
<p>Skip to:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#core">Core page types</a></li>
<li><a href="#extended">Additional page types</a></li>
<li><a href="#academia">Academic page types (not related to education)</a></li>
<li><a href="#education">Page types related to education</a></li>
<li><a href="#research-data-management">Pages releated to research data management</a></li>
<li><a href="#uk">Page types for UK organisations</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Example of Use</h2>
<div class='code'>
&lt;http://id.southampton.ac.uk/&gt; 
   foaf:homepage &lt;http://www.soton.ac.uk/&gt; ;
   lyou:events &lt;http://www.events.soton.ac.uk/&gt; ;
   lyou:research &lt;https://www.soton.ac.uk/research/index.shtml&gt; .
</div>

<h2>Changelog</h2>
<h3>2013-01-29</h3>
<ul>
<li>Added comments to clarify several fields</li>
<li>Added lyou:legal-ethics</li>
<li>added terms for lyou:postgraduate-research and lyou:postgraduate-taught (and the related courses, prospectus and entry-requirement terms)</li>
<li>deprecated less lyou:postgraduate-courses, lyou:postgraduate-prospectus, lyou:postgradute-entry-requirements as these are too vague.</li>
<li>changed description of lyou:postgraduate to mean a general postgraduate admissions page, usually linking to both research and taught posgraduate admissions.</li>
</ul>

<h3>2013-10-01</h3>
<ul>
<li>Added lyou:web-accessibility.</li>
<li>Added lyou:space-accessibility.</li>
<li>Added lyou:uk-ico-publication-scheme.</li>
<li>Added new section for UK-specific terms.</li>
</ul>
<h3>2016-05-20</h3>
<ul>
<li>Added research data management section. These terms were defined in a project with the UK <a href='http://www.dcc.ac.uk/'>Digital Curation Centre</a>.</li>
<li>Added 'research repository' to the 'academa' section.</li>
</ul>



<a name='core'></a><h2>Core Page Properties</h2><dl><dt>Property: foaf:homepage</dt><dd><em>homepage</em> - FOAF already defines a perfectly good way to indicate a homepage.<div class='uri'>URI: http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/homepage</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:events</dt><dd><em>events page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/events</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:business</dt><dd><em>business page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/business</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:depts</dt><dd><em>departments page</em> - Links a group or organisation to a document describing its parts. This is not a linkingyou term but was added as the existing terms were only applicable to academia.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/depts</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:about</dt><dd><em>about page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/about</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:search</dt><dd><em>search page</em> - Perhaps this should link to a string with a variable in to indicate how to construct a search?<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/search</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:press</dt><dd><em>press page</em> - A page with information specifically aimed at journalists.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/press</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:news</dt><dd><em>news page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/news</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:jobs</dt><dd><em>jobs page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/jobs</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal</dt><dd><em>legal page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:contact</dt><dd><em>contact page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/contact</div></dd></dl><a name='extended'></a><h2>Additional Page Properties</h2><dl><dt>Property: lyou:about-leader</dt><dd><em>leader page</em> - Links a group or organisation to a page about the leader of that organisation. This is modified from the linkingyou 'vc' page to make it work for organistations where the leader is not a Vice Chancellor.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/about-leader</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:about-executive</dt><dd><em>executive page</em> - Links a group or organisation to a page about the senior staff, be it Microsoft's senior staff or the committee members of a university club. This was not a linkingyou term.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/about-executive</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:about-strategy</dt><dd><em>strategy page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/about-strategy</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:about-sites</dt><dd><em>sites page</em> - Links a group or organisation to a page about the sites or campuses of that organisation. Was about/campuses in linkingyou, but altered here to be less academic-only.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/about-sites</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:press-facts</dt><dd><em>press facts page</em> - A page aimed at the press with a list of useful facts about the organisation.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/press-facts</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-policies</dt><dd><em>policies page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-policies</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-data-protection</dt><dd><em>data-protection statement page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-data-protection</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-environment</dt><dd><em>environmental policy page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-environment</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-equality</dt><dd><em>equality policy page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-equality</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-foi</dt><dd><em>freedom-of-information policy page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-foi</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-ict</dt><dd><em>ICT policy page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-ict</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-website</dt><dd><em>website legal information page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-website</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-regulations</dt><dd><em>regulations page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-regulations</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:contact-staff</dt><dd><em>staff contact page</em> - A page giving contact details for staff in the organisation. Generally this is a searchable phonebook.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/contact-staff</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:ict-support</dt><dd><em>ICT support page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/ict-support</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:open-data</dt><dd><em>open data page</em> - Links a group or organisation to a page (or the homepage of a website) describing open data services from the organisation, eg. http://data.lincoln.ac.uk/<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/open-data</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:web-accessibility</dt><dd><em>web accessibility</em> - Links a group or organisation to a document which describes the accessibility policy of the organisation regarding websites and online resources. May also be used to link the homepage of a website to an accessibility document.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/web-accessibility</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:space-accessibility</dt><dd><em>spatial acessibility</em> - Links a group or organisation to a document describing the aspects of the location and environment of this organisation. Generally this will be for the benefit of a visitor with a physical or mental disability. May also be used to link a spatial thing (such as a building, airport, campus, bus) to a description of its accessibility.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/space-accessibility</div></dd></dl><a name='academia'></a><h2>Academic Page Properties</h2><p>These page types are not strictly limited to universities. Non-academic organisations may do research or have converences.</p><dl><dt>Property: lyou:research</dt><dd><em>research page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:legal-ethics</dt><dd><em>ethics policy</em> - Many research organisations have a public ethics policy.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/legal-ethics</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:conferences</dt><dd><em>conferences page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/conferences</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:public-lectures</dt><dd><em>public lectures page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/public-lectures</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:business-incubation</dt><dd><em>business incubation page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/business-incubation</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:business-ktp</dt><dd><em>business knowlege transfer partnerships page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/business-ktp</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:academic-depts</dt><dd><em>academic departments page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/academic-depts</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:support-depts</dt><dd><em>support departments page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/support-depts</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:conference-facilities</dt><dd><em>conference facilities page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/conference-facilities</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-repository</dt><dd><em>Institutional research publications and outputs repository</em> - The homepgage of a repository used by this organisation for research outputs. This does not link to a URI or a OAI-PMH interface. Other vocabularies do that.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-repository</div></dd></dl><a name='education'></a><h2>Education Page Properties</h2><dl><dt>Property: lyou:courses</dt><dd><em>courses page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/courses</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:undergraduate</dt><dd><em>undergraduate admissions page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/undergraduate</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:undergraduate-courses</dt><dd><em>undergraduate courses page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/undergraduate-courses</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:undergraduate-courses-entry-requirements</dt><dd><em>undergraduate courses entry requirements page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/undergraduate-courses-entry-requirements</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:undergraduate-prospectus</dt><dd><em>undergraduate prospectus page</em> - Link a university, or other degree awarding organisation, to its undergraduate prospectus. This may be an HTML or PDF document.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/undergraduate-prospectus</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate</dt><dd><em>general postgraduate admissions page</em> - covering research and taught postgraduates<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-taught</dt><dd><em>taught postgraduate admissions page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-taught</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-taught-courses</dt><dd><em>taught postgraduate courses page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-taught-courses</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-taught-courses-entry-requirements</dt><dd><em>taught postgraduate entry requirements page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-taught-courses-entry-requirements</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-taught-prospectus</dt><dd><em>taught postgraduate prospectus page</em> - Link a university, or other degree awarding organisation, to its taught postgraduate prospectus. This may be an HTML or PDF document.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-taught-prospectus</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-research</dt><dd><em>research postgraduate admissions page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-research</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-research-courses</dt><dd><em>research postgraduate courses (or programmes) page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-research-courses</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-research-courses-entry-requirements</dt><dd><em>research postgraduate entry requirements page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-research-courses-entry-requirements</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:postgraduate-research-prospectus</dt><dd><em>research postgraduate prospectus page</em> - Link a university, or other degree awarding organisation, to its research postgraduate prospectus. This may be an HTML or PDF document.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/postgraduate-research-prospectus</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:foundation</dt><dd><em>foundation admissions page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/foundation</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:foundation-courses</dt><dd><em>foundation courses page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/foundation-courses</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:foundation-courses-entry-requirements</dt><dd><em>foundation courses entry requirements page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/foundation-courses-entry-requirements</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:foundation-prospectus</dt><dd><em>foundation prospectus page</em> - Link a university, or other degree awarding organisation, to its foundation prospectus. This may be an HTML or PDF document.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/foundation-prospectus</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:opendays</dt><dd><em>open days page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/opendays</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:events-graduation</dt><dd><em>graduation event page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/events-graduation</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:about-parents</dt><dd><em>information for parents page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/about-parents</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:international-students</dt><dd><em>information for international students page</em><div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/international-students</div></dd></dl><a name='research-data-management'></a><h2>Research Data Management Properties</h2><p>These terms link to web pages (or other online documents) describing an organisation's research data management policies and infrastructure.</p><dl><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-funders-policies</dt><dd><em>Research data funders' policies</em> - An information page (or pages) on funders' policies. This could be internal or external (E.g., DCC's policy overview table). This is the policies of organistations that fund research data at the subject organisation.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-funders-policies</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-policy</dt><dd><em>Research data policy</em> - An organisation's research data policy or aspirational statement.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-policy</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-strategy</dt><dd><em>Strategy or implementation plan for research data services</em> - An organisation's research data strategy page or roadmap.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-strategy</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-management-support</dt><dd><em>RDM advice and support services</em> - A document describing research data management planning guidance and/or support services at this organisation<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-management-support</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-active-storage</dt><dd><em>Active research data storage</em> - A document describing active research data storage used by this organisation. Is likely to have multiple values.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-active-storage</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-catalogue</dt><dd><em>Data register or catalogue</em> - A, possibly internal, research data registration homepage. This may be provided via the data repository and/or Current Research Information System (CRIS). This predicate does not provide a link into any APIs or data.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-catalogue</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-item-identifier-scheme-definition</dt><dd><em>Research data identification scheme definition</em> - A document detailing a scheme or schemes schemes used to identify digital data items (e.g., DataCite). Where available this should be the formal definition document, otherwise the homepage.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-item-identifier-scheme-definition</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-access</dt><dd><em>Research data access procedures</em> - A document providing information about research data access at this organisation.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-access</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-secure-access</dt><dd><em>Secure research data access</em> - Document describing the organisation's secure research data access and governance.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-secure-access</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-repository</dt><dd><em>Research data repository</em> - Provide a link to the research data repository being used to provide short to mid-term access to research data beyond the life of a project. This may or may not be the same as the repository for longer term access or preservation.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-repository</div></dd><dt>Property: lyou:research-data-repository-long-term</dt><dd><em>Long-term Research data repository</em> - The homepage of a repository used by this organisation for long-term research data.This may be an extension of the publications repository, a separate data repository or a pointer to an external data repository service (E.g., Zenodo).<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/research-data-repository-long-term</div></dd></dl><a name='uk'></a><h2>UK-Specific Page Properties</h2><p>These pages are only really useful for UK organsations.</p><dl><dt>Property: lyou:uk-ico-publication-scheme</dt><dd><em>ICO publication scheme</em> - [Generally only for UK public sector] A link to the publication scheme for this organisation as described by the UK Information Commissioner's Office. See http://www.ico.org.uk/for_organisations/freedom_of_information/guide/publication_scheme for more information.<div class='uri'>URI: http://purl.org/linkingyou/uk-ico-publication-scheme</div></dd></dl>    </body>
</html>
